---
title: Installation
description: How to install {{ project_name }}
---

## From crates.io

```bash
cargo install {{ project_name }}
```

## From source

```bash
git clone https://github.com/{{ owner }}/{{ project_name }}.git
cd {{ project_name }}
cargo install --path crates/{{ project_name }}
```

## Pre-built binaries

Download the latest release for your platform from the
[releases page](https://github.com/{{ owner }}/{{ project_name }}/releases).

## Verify installation

```bash
{{ project_name }} --version
```
